+# Pruned
+
+- Format registry / exporter base class / strategy or plugin system for export
+  formats. Reason: only ONE format (JSON) is required now. csv/markdown are
+  speculative ("probably later"); the discipline forbids the abstraction until
+  at least two formats are actually required. A second format, when real, is a
+  trivial branch — no premature indirection.
+- Adding an `export`/`dump` helper in `store.py`. Reason: `store.load` already
+  returns the serializable list; a wrapper adds a layer without behavior.
