@@ -0,0 +1,18 @@
+# Corridor: DA1-B-export
+
+## Goal Frontier
+- `python3 -m cli_notes.cli --store <file> export <outfile>` writes `<outfile>`
+  whose contents are a JSON array of the notes.
+- `python3 -m unittest` passes from the project directory.
+
+## Start Frontier
+- `cli_notes/store.py::load(path)` already returns the notes as a list of dicts.
+- `cli_notes/cli.py::build_parser()` wires subcommands; `cmd_add`/`cmd_list`
+  are the handler pattern to follow. `main()` dispatches via `args.func`.
+
+## Meeting Corridor
+The notes are already a JSON-serializable list and `store.load` returns them,
+so export is one `json.dump(store.load(...))`. Only the CLI changes.
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
